transcript:
[Ringing]
Executive: Hello.
Executive: Hello. Good afternoon sir, Ashutosh baat kar raha hu India Mart se.
Executive: Aapko call aaya sir? Ashutosh baat kar raha hu India Mart se. Ye aapka call aaya hai kabhi?
Customer: Koi aaya hoga sir, abhi aapne drop kiya.
Executive: Achha jaldi se lag gaya tha.
Executive: Hain?
Executive: Jaldi se call lag gaya tha. Abhi 2 baje kareeb aaya tha aapka call. Yaad nahi?
